Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:37.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願っても何もできないと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:39.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}わかってはいるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:42.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}失う怖さが邪魔をしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:44.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}誰しも明日へ向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:46.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}見えない 知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:49.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}自由も愛も与えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:53.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}さぁ選べ  舞い降りた天使達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}感じる予感に Shoot the arrow of fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}翼に意志を 身を委ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:02.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}倦まず弛まず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:05.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}ただ 生きてたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:07.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}もう いっそ嘘でもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:10.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}正義を貫く 最後で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:13.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}「幸せになりたい」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:21.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}ただそれだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}It ain’t over till it’s over(Shoot!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}勇往邁進 GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:37.49,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}即使祈願 也什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:39.37,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}明明知道如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:42.08,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}哪怕失去的恐懼作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:44.54,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}人們還是會走向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:46.71,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}看不見 不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:49.17,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}給他自由與愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:53.30,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}好了 選擇吧 飛舞降臨的天使們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.22,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}向察覺的預感 射出命運之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.72,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}灌注意志於翅膀  委身於它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:02.97,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}不知疲倦 從不鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:05.31,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}只是 想要活著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:07.94,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}不管了 就算撒謊也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:10.23,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}貫穿正義 到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:13.15,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}說一句「我想要幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:21.66,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.91,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}它不會結束 直到它結束 (發射!!)
