Comment: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:54.09,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,還記得那甜美的氣息
Comment: 0,0:22:54.09,0:22:56.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,秘密箱庭之中
Comment: 0,0:22:57.31,0:23:00.42,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不抱懷疑的等待
