Comment: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:10.26,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,平行世界的終焉
Comment: 0,0:23:10.26,0:23:16.16,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,窺探也不會改變
Comment: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,早餐拭淚的兩人
Comment: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:25.98,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,那之外確切的事情
Comment: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:32.98,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了能夠喘息的一切
Comment: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:39.19,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,如能無需背負
Comment: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:45.23,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,蓋住我的眼睛
Comment: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:49.45,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,說變得幸福吧
Comment: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:55.27,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,但不可靠的體溫
